10-0.query:
SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS uncredited_voiced_character, MIN(t.title) AS russian_movie
FROM sampled_char_name_4 AS chn,
 sampled_cast_info_4 AS ci,
 sampled_company_name_4 AS cn,
 sampled_company_type_4 AS ct,
 sampled_movie_companies_4 AS mc,
 sampled_role_type_4 AS rt,
 sampled_title_4 AS t
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND t.id = ci.movie_id
 AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
 AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
 AND rt.id = ci.role_id
 AND cn.id = mc.company_id
 AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
AND ci.note LIKE '@param0'
AND ci.note LIKE '@param1'
AND cn.country_code = '@param2'
AND rt.role = '@param3'
AND t.production_year > @param4;
